        <h2>Haas: Mick Schumacher looks like Michael</h2>
        <p>
            Mick Schumacher, the son of seven-time world champion Michael Schumacher, will make his Formula 1 debut this year. Mick will be driving for Haas, which emerged after Schumacher Sr. left F1.
However, Haas ' close cooperation with Ferrari led to the fact that there are employees in the American team who found Michael in the Scuderia. And according to Haas boss Gunther Steiner, Schumacher Jr. seems like a father figure to them.
"I had never worked with Michael and I didn't know him very well," Steiner said. I only heard that he worked very hard." We have a few people in the team from Ferrari who worked there with Michael. They were very emotional about Mick's arrival. They explained how Michael worked, and I think Mick is very similar to him.
He works hard, wants to know everything, wants to learn, to get better every day, every hour, every minute."
        </p>
