        <p>Fernando Alonso has returned to Formula 1 after a two-year hiatus and will compete in the middle of the peloton at the wheel of the Alpine.The 39-year-old admits that the competition in the championship is now very high, but he is confident that he surpasses all rivals in skill.

"I look forward to meeting the young talents who performed well in the junior categories," Alonso said. – And then there are all these champions: Lewis, Sebastian, Kimi. And Verstappen, who, although from a new generation, has been playing at the top level for several years.

